https://www.npr.org/2010/12/06/131812500/israel-kamakawiwo-ole-the-voice-of-hawaii</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JGzyPlx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Genius grandma!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DC1Trcy</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GwQX7jt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DC1Trcy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hockeybrat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>remember juice?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/beofqyR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/X6UsPep.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/beofqyR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aap71]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>day unruined?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mHc2ahy</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IPA3ODI.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>follow up from: https://imgur.com/gallery/r6GCRYf</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mHc2ahy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Broke down outside the store</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EO8seB3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/irOSWkC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I have been living on almost nothing for 2 months now, been job hunting like crazy, have few interviews coming up this week and the next, but man this time has been heavy financially for me. I managed to do some surveys and get about 20 EUR to my account, I was going to get some small groceries for it to last me few days when my card failed at the check out. Apperently my bank took a fee giving me 3 EUR left.

As my card wouldnt work I told them to put the stuff aside as I didnt have any other payment options and apologized for the inconveniance. This woman behind me told me she wanted to pay for it.

I had to really push myself to not start crying there and then, and I could tell she understood my frustration. She just said "we've all been there. pay it forward in the future".

I expressed my greatest gratitude and walked out of the store with my food.

On the 30 min walk home I couldn't stop crying, luckily no one saw me.

Any gesture can mean the world to someone in need. I cant even describe how much this woman means to me. I feel like what she did made my entire decade.

Take care of yourself out there, be nice to each others.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EO8seB3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jockeeeeeeee]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JZ5OmDd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1vrxwnr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JZ5OmDd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[lifonaut]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Superior cut of Twilight</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NWGb0vh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yI8PwLm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Snapchat filters. Gone too far or not far enough?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NWGb0vh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[UncleToot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wait for it.....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WtTQ4KP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pnx94VU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The right, with their love of cancel culture, is sure to be calling for the obliteration of "The Simpsons" after last night's episode, "Poorhouse Rock", dropped a nuclear sized bomb on right wing politics.  It was beautiful and scary.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WtTQ4KP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DCon101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing surprising here ....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/L3Wf23x</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/um91hSf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/L3Wf23x</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I see said the blind man ....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TVyhBa7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt=""